{
  "page": "Feature quote/221",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Are you good or evil, my lady?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a><br />“Oh, good. I am a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of sorts myself, sweet ser. A champion of light and life.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406123925\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 106/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 298/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.126      1 -total\n100.00%    5.126      1 Template:Ref\n 68.30%    3.501      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26663-0!canonical and timestamp 20260406123925 and revision id 243818\n -->\n",
